## Public RPCs for Ethereum, BSC, and Polygon

Users can immediately take advantage of bitindi's frontrunning protection/prevention features by routing their transactions through bitindiâ€™s RPC inside their wallets. bitindi currently has the following RPCs available for users:

|  Network Name   | Blockchain  | Chain ID    | Region  | RPC URL  |

| ---------------  | -------------  |----------   | --------- | ----------- |
| ETH Protect   | Ethereum  |1  | Multi | https://ethpro.bitindi.org |
